  api.fillList('requisitionDescriptionInterface', 'descRequisition', ['186356','true','186356','false','Submission for the position: Lockwood Bartender (Part-Time) - (Job Number: FOO016YV)','false','186356','false','true','https://hilton.taleo.net/careersection/jobdetail.ftl?job=FOO016YV%26lang=en','Lockwood Bartender (Part-Time)','true','Lockwood Bartender (Part-Time)','FOO016YV','FOO016YV','%3CBR%3E%3CSPAN class=%27text%27 style=%27padding-left: 6px;%27%3EThe Palmer House Hilton%3C/SPAN%3E%3CSPAN class=%27text%27 style=%27padding-left: 6px;%27%3E (04087)%3C/SPAN%3E%3CBR%3E%3CSPAN class=%27text%27 style=%27padding-left: 6px;%27%3E17 East Monroe Street%3C/SPAN%3E%3CBR%3E%3CSPAN class=%27text%27 style=%27padding-left: 6px;%27%3EChicago%3C/SPAN%3E, %3CSPAN class=%27text%27 style=%27padding-left: 6px;%27%3E60603%3C/SPAN%3E%3CBR%3E%3CBR%3E','The Palmer House Hilton','17 East Monroe Street','','Chicago','60603','!*!A Bartender with Hilton Hotels and Resorts is responsible for preparing beverages and serving beverages and/or food to guests in the hotelÆs continuing effort to deliver outstanding guest service and financial profitability.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cb%3EWhat will it be like to work for this Hilton Worldwide Brand?%3C/b%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOne of the most recognized names in the industry, Hilton Hotels %26 Resorts offers travelers a world of authentic experiences. Hilton remains an innovative, forward-thinking hospitality leader by offering best-in-class products, services and amenities to ensure that every guest feels cared for, valued and respected. From inaugural balls and international award galas to business events and personal moments, Hilton is where the world makes history, closes the deal, toasts special occasions and gets away from it all.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHilton Hotels %26 Resorts is one of Hilton WorldwideÆs ten market-leading brands. For more information visit www.hiltonworldwide.com.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIf you understand the importance of upholding a brandÆs reputation and what it takes to provide a globally recognized hospitality experience, you may be just the person we are looking for to work as a Team Member with Hilton Hotels %26 Resorts. %3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cb%3EWhat will I be doing?%3C/b%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cp%3EAs a Bartender, you would be responsible for preparing beverages and serving beverages and/or food to guests in the hotelÆs continuing effort to deliver outstanding guest service and financial profitability. Specifically, you would be responsible for performing the following tasks to the highest standards:%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cul%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EGreet guests and respond to guest inquiries and requests in a timely, friendly and efficient manner%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EMix and garnish beverages according to recipe and portion control standards%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EPresent and serve beverages to guests%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ECheck guests for proper identification and serve alcoholic beverages to guests in accordance with federal, state, local and company laws and regulations%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EAccurately total, process and collect payments from guests to include, but not limited to, using the point-of-sale system, handling money, processing credit and debit cards, making change and processing gift certificates, cards and vouchers%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EStock and maintain the bar to include, but not limited to, beer, wine, spirits, paper products, straws and stirrers, condiments, glassware, ice and produce%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ECut, store and ensure product quality of all beverage-related perishables%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ERespond professionally to inebriated guests, as needed%3Ca name=%22%22OLE_LINK1%22%22 id=%22%22OLE_LINK1%22%22%3E%3C/a%3E%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A  %3C/ul%3E','!*!%3Cb%3EWhat are we looking for?%3C/b%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A %3Cp%3ESince being founded in 1919, Hilton Worldwide has been a leader in the hospitality industry. Today, Hilton Worldwide remains a beacon of innovation, quality, and success. This continued leadership is the result of our Team Members staying true to our Vision, Mission, and Values. Specifically, we look for demonstration of these Values:%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EH%3C/strong%3E Hospitality - We%26#x0027;re passionate about delivering exceptional guest experiences.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%3C/strong%3E Integrity - We do the right thing, all the time.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EL%3C/strong%3E Leadership - We%26#x0027;re leaders in our industry and in our communities.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ET%3C/strong%3E Teamwork - We%26#x0027;re team players in everything we do.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EO%3C/strong%3E Ownership - We%26#x0027;re the owners of our actions and decisions.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EN%3C/strong%3E Now - We operate with a sense of urgency and discipline%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3EIn addition, we look for the demonstration of the following key attributes in our Team Members:%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cul%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ELiving the Values%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EQuality%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EProductivity%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EDependability%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ECustomer Focus%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ETeamwork%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EAdaptability%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A  %3C/ul%3E%0A  %3Cbr%3E%0A  %3Cb%3EWhat benefits will I receive?%3C/b%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A  Your benefits will include a competitive starting salary and, depending upon eligibility, a vacation or Paid Time Off (PTO) benefit.  You will instantly have access to our unique benefits such as the Team Member and Family T