  api.fillList('requisitionDescriptionInterface', 'descRequisition', ['184149','true','184149','false','Submission for the position: Line Cook - (Job Number: KIC012C8)','false','184149','false','true','https://hilton.taleo.net/careersection/jobdetail.ftl?job=KIC012C8%26lang=en','Line Cook','true','Line Cook','KIC012C8','KIC012C8','%3CBR%3E%3CSPAN class=%27text%27 style=%27padding-left: 6px;%27%3EEmbassy Suites Chicago - Lombard/Oak Brook%3C/SPAN%3E%3CSPAN class=%27text%27 style=%27padding-left: 6px;%27%3E (69514)%3C/SPAN%3E%3CBR%3E%3CSPAN class=%27text%27 style=%27padding-left: 6px;%27%3E707 E. Butterfield Rd%3C/SPAN%3E%3CBR%3E%3CSPAN class=%27text%27 style=%27padding-left: 6px;%27%3ELombard%3C/SPAN%3E, %3CSPAN class=%27text%27 style=%27padding-left: 6px;%27%3E60148%3C/SPAN%3E%3CBR%3E%3CBR%3E','Embassy Suites Chicago - Lombard/Oak Brook','707 E. Butterfield Rd','','Lombard','60148','!*!A Cook with Embassy Suites Hotels is responsible for preparing food items in accordance with recipes and established standards %3Ca name=%22%22OLE_LINK5%22%22 id=%22%22OLE_LINK5%22%22%3E%3C/a%3Ein the hotelÆs continuing effort to deliver outstanding service and financial profitability.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cb%3EWhat will it be like to work for this Hilton Worldwide Brand?%3C/b%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EEmbassy Suites by Hilton has perfected the full-service, upscale, all-suite hotel. Built on a long-standing legacy that is both inviting and comfortable, Embassy Suites properties provide guests with ôMore Reasons to Stay«,ö offering open-air atriums, complimentary cooked-to-order breakfast, spacious two-room suites and complimentary ManagerÆs Receptions every evening. Embassy SuitesÆ bundled pricing ensures that guests receive enormous value at a single price. Whether they are traveling for business, with their family, with a group, or for leisure, our guests return again and again to experience the consistently awarded, best-in-class customer service provided at Embassy Suites.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EEmbassy Suites is one of Hilton WorldwideÆs ten market-leading brands. For more information visit www.hiltonworldwide.com%0A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIf you understand the importance of providing an inviting and comfortable experience and feel you can contribute to an award-winning team, you may be just the person we are looking for to work as a Team Member with Embassy Suites Hotels.  %0A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cb%3EWhat will I be doing?%3C/b%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cp%3EAs a Cook, you would be responsible for preparing food items in accordance with recipes and established standards in the hotelÆs continuing effort to deliver outstanding service and financial profitability. Specifically, you would be responsible for performing the following tasks to the highest standards:%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cul%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EPrepare food items according to designated recipes and quality standards%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EMaintain cleanliness and comply with food sanitation standards at all times%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EManage guest orders in a friendly, timely and efficient manner%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EEnsure knowledge of menu and all food products%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EStock and maintain designated food station(s)%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EVisually inspect all food sent from the kitchen%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EPractice correct food handling and food storage procedures according to federal, state, local and company regulations%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EPrepare requisitions for supplies and food items, as needed%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A  %3C/ul%3E','!*!%3Cb%3EWhat are we looking for?%3C/b%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A %3Cp%3ESince being founded in 1919, Hilton Worldwide has been a leader in the hospitality industry. Today, Hilton Worldwide remains a beacon of innovation, quality, and success. This continued leadership is the result of our Team Members staying true to our Vision, Mission, and Values. Specifically, we look for demonstration of these Values:%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EH%3C/strong%3E Hospitality - We%26#x0027;re passionate about delivering exceptional guest experiences.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%3C/strong%3E Integrity - We do the right thing, all the time.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EL%3C/strong%3E Leadership - We%26#x0027;re leaders in our industry and in our communities.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ET%3C/strong%3E Teamwork - We%26#x0027;re team players in everything we do.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EO%3C/strong%3E Ownership - We%26#x0027;re the owners of our actions and decisions.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EN%3C/strong%3E Now - We operate with a sense of urgency and discipline%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3EIn addition, we look for the demonstration of the following key attributes in our Team Members:%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cul%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ELiving the Values%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EQuality%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EProductivity%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EDependability%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ECustomer Focus%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ETeamwork%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EAdaptability%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A  %3C/ul%3E%0A  %3Cbr%3E%0A  %3Cb%3EWhat benefits will I receive?%3C/b%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A  Your benefits will include a competitive starting salary and, depending upon eligibility, a vacation or Paid Time Off (PTO) benefit.  You will instantly have access to our unique benefits such as the Team Member and Family Travel Program, which provides reduced hotel room rates at many of our hotels for you and your family, plus discounts on products and services offered by Hilton Worldwide and its partners.  After 90 days you may enroll in Hilton WorldwideÆs Health %26 Welfare benefit plans, depending on eligibility.  Hilton Worldwide also offers eligible team members a 401K Savings Plan, as well as Employee Assistance and Educational Assistance Programs.  We look forward to reviewing with you the specific benefits you would receive as a Hilton Worldwide Team Member.  The above information is provided as a highlight of the major benefits offered to most full-team team members in the United States.  All benefits listed may not be offered at all locations.  This is not a summary plan description or official plan document.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cb%3EEOE/AA%3C/b%3E','!*!%3Cb%3EWhat are we looking for?%3C/b%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A %3Cp%3ESince being founded in 1919, Hilton Worldwide has been a leader in the hospitality industry. Today, Hilton Worldwide remains a beacon of innovation, quality, and success. This continued leadership is the result of our Team Members staying true to our Vision, Mission, and Values. Specifically, we look for demonstration of these Values:%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EH%3C/strong%3E Hospitality - We%26#x0027;re passionate about delivering exceptional guest experiences.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%3C/strong%3E Integrity - We do the right thing, all the time.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EL%3C/strong%3E Leadership - We%26#x0027;re leaders in our industry and in our communities.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ET%3C/strong%3E Teamwork - We%26#x0027;re team players in everything we do.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EO%3C/strong%3E Ownership - We%26#x0027;re the owners of our actions and decisions.%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EN%3C/strong%3E Now - We operate with a sense of urgency and discipline%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cp%3EIn addition, we look for the demonstration of the following key attributes in our Team Members:%3C/p%3E%0A  %3Cul%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ELiving the Values%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EQuality%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EProductivity%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EDependability%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ECustomer Focus%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3ETeamwork%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A    %3Cli%3E%0A      %3Cp%3EAdaptability%3C/p%3E%0A    %3C/li%3E%0A  %3C/ul%3E%0A  %3Cbr%3E%0A  %3Cb%3EWhat benefits will I receive?%3C/b%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A  Your benefits will include a competitive starting salary and, depending upon eligibility, a vacation or Paid Time Off (PTO) benefit.  You will instantly have access to our unique benefits such as the Team Member and Family Travel Program, which provides reduced hotel room rates at many of our hotels for you and your family, plus discounts on products and services offered by Hilton Worldwide and its partners.  After 90 days you may enroll in Hilton WorldwideÆs Health %26 Welfare benefit plans, depending on eligibility.  Hilton Worldwide also offers eligible team members a 401K Savings Plan, as well as Employee Assistance and Educational Assistance Programs.  We look forward to reviewing with you the specific benefits you would receive as a Hilton Worldwide Team Member.  The above information is provided as a highlight of the major benefits offered to most full-team team members in the United States.  All benefits listed may not be offered at all locations.  This is not a summary plan description or official plan document.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cb%3EEOE/AA%3C/b%3E','Culinary','Culinary','Full-time','Full-time','Embassy Suites Hotels','Embassy Suites Hotels','Full Availability','Full Availability','Team Member','Team Member','false','184149','184149','true','184149','false','Submission for the position: Line Cook - (Job Number: KIC012C8)','false','184149','false','true','https://hilton.taleo.net/careersection/jobdetail.ftl?job=KIC012C8%26lang=en','Line Cook','true']);
